  "title": "Legal Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><ol><li>To assist Head of Legal to draft, review and amend various types of contracts and agreements.</li><li>To assist Head of Legal to liaise with external lawyers for dispute resolution.</li><li>To assist Head of Legal to provide legal consultation and support to various business departments within the company.</li><li>To assist Head of Legal to verify the compliance of various business departments of relevant business\nregulations and procedures.</li><li>To Complete other tasks assigned by the department head.</li></ol><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ol><li>Bachelor's degree or higher is compulsory.</li><li>Major in Law is preferred.</li><li>Fluent oral as well as written English and Chinese languages.</li></ol>",
